doctype transitional
html(xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml')
  head
    meta(http-equiv='Content-Type', content='text/html; charset=UTF-8')
    title *|MC:SUBJECT|*
    style
      include style.css
  body(leftmargin='0', marginwidth='0', topmargin='0', marginheight='0', offset='0')
    center
      table#bodyTable(align='center', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0', height='100%', width='100%')
        tbody
          tr
            td#bodyCell(align='center', valign='top')
              // BEGIN TEMPLATE //
              table#templateContainer(border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
                tbody
                  tr
                    td(align='center', valign='top')
                      // BEGIN HEADER //
                      table#templateHeader(border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0', width='100%')
                        tbody
                          tr
                            td.headerContent(valign='top')
                              img#headerImage(src=emailHeaderImage, style='max-width:600px;', mc:label='header_image', mc:edit='header_image', mc:allowdesigner='', mc:allowtext='')
                      // // END HEADER
                  tr
                    td(align='center', valign='top')
                      // BEGIN BODY //
                      table#templateBody(border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0', width='100%')
                        tbody
                          tr
                            td.bodyContent(valign='top', style='text-align: left', mc:edit='body_content00')
                              h3 Dear #{user}!
                              p Thank you for registering as a <strong> Data Partner with SMART MOVE </strong> Innovative Urban Mobility Challenge. For easy reference, please find attached your submitted form in an editable .docx format. 
                              
                              strong To complete your registration, follow these 3 simple steps
                              ol
                                li <strong>Login to our secure file sharing platform</strong> #{pydioUrl} using the username and password below. 
                                |  Username: #{username}
                                br
                                |  Password: #{password}
                                li Once you login, <strong>drag and drop the files you wish to share </strong> into their sector-wise folders on the webpage. You can also use the ‘New’ button on the top left corner to upload files and folders from your computer. 
                                li Please ensure you <strong>share the data in a machine-readable format </strong> (.xls, .csv, JSON, etc.). 
                              p We assure you that all <strong>the data that you share will be securely stored</strong> at the National Institute of Urban Affairs for the duration of the Challenge. We will <strong>only share it with registered participants </strong> with an <strong>attached data license</strong> that clearly states the terms and conditions of use. 

                              p To learn more about the data sharing process, please visit our Frequently Asked Questions page here #{faqUrl}
                              
                                p Do you have any other questions about the file sharing process or the SMART MOVE Challenge? Reach out to us at <u> smartmove@niua.org </u> or speak to Mr. Ankit Rai at +91 1124634971 (ext. 219). 
                              
                                p Thank you for helping India take another step towards smart and sustainable urban mobility. 
                              
                            tr
                            td.bodyContent(valign='top', style='text-align: left', mc:edit='body_content00')
                              | Kind regards ,<br>
                              | The #{hackathonName} Team
                      // // END BODY
                  tr
                    td(align='center', valign='top')
                      // BEGIN FOOTER //
                      table#templateFooter(border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0', width='100%')
                        tbody
                          tr
                            td.footerContent(valign='top', mc:edit='footer_content00')
                              a(href='https://twitter.com/' + twitterHandle) Follow on Twitter&nbsp;
                              a(href='mailto:#{emailAddress}') Email Us
                          tr
                            td.footerContent(valign='top', style='padding-top:0;', mc:edit='footer_content01')
                              em Copyright © #{hackathonName} 2020, All rights reserved.
                              br
                      // // END FOOTER
                      // // END TEMPLATE
